.TH VDR-SUITE-DAEMON 8 "Phase 56" "vdr-suite" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
vdr-suite-daemon \- runtime daemon for vdr-suite
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vdr-suite-daemon
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B vdr-suite-daemon
is the runtime service process for vdr-suite.

It exposes the vdr-suite runtime API and coordinates configured VDR backends through the internal service and adapter architecture.
.SH CONFIGURATION
The default configuration file is planned as:
.PP
.I /etc/vdr-suite/vdr-suite.conf
.PP
The exact configuration keys are defined by the runtime configuration contract and may evolve before Debian packaging is introduced.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/vdr-suite/vdr-suite.conf
Runtime configuration file.
.TP
.I /usr/sbin/vdr-suite-daemon
Daemon binary.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vdr-suite.conf (5),
.BR vdr-suite-dashboard (1)
.SH STATUS
This manual page is an initial Phase 56 skeleton for packaging-readiness work.
